http://code.google.com/p/ganeti/

Tuto d'installation :
http://docs.ganeti.org/ganeti/current/html/install.html


Installé Ganeti :

/etc/hosts doit resembler à ça :

127.0.0.1       localhost
192.0.2.1     node1.example.com node1

 192.0.2.1 with your node’s address. Also, the file /etc/hostname which configures the hostname of the system should contain node1.example.com and not just node1 (you need to run the command /etc/init.d/hostname.sh start after changing the file) .

En remplacent 192.0.2.1 par l'adresse du node.
Le fichier /etc/hostname doit contenir node1.exemple.com et pas seulement node1 (Il faudra executer la commance /etc/init.d/hostnames.sh start).




